   377→## Caveats
   382→By default, `input-otp` handles password managers for you.
   383→The password manager badges should be automatically shifted to the right side.
   384→
   385→However, if you still want to block password managers, please disable the `pushPasswordManagerStrategy` and then manually block each PWM.
   386→
